33:01.437 --> 33:02.272
David, I'm just

33:02.438 --> 33:03.922
a little... I don't know...

33:04.047 --> 33:06.547
confused about
your participation here.

33:09.737 --> 33:11.323
And, hey, wasn't
that number fantastic

33:11.489 --> 33:12.991
and truly authentic?

33:14.991 --> 33:16.536
Thank you very much, everyone.

33:16.702 --> 33:18.788
Now, if you'll excuse me,
I have a stack of

33:18.954 --> 33:20.582
night school exams on my desk

33:20.748 --> 33:23.335
that won't grade themselves,
so <i>buenas noches</i>.

33:23.501 --> 33:24.127
<i>Muchas gracias.</i>

33:24.293 --> 33:25.253
Bye-bye.

33:25.419 --> 33:27.756
Well, Mr. Shue,
the floor is all yours.

33:27.922 --> 33:30.382
